descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... a number of red lines which create smaller black shapes
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input grid
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... fill the largest black shape with dark blue. Fill the smallest black shape with light blue. If there is more than one shape with the smallest number of squares, fill all of the smallest shapes with light blue.
